WEBVTT

00:07:59.007 --> 00:08:01.557
being all supportive
and thankful for our willingness

00:08:01.581 --> 00:08:04.193
to care for the beauty
and the environment of Bali.

00:08:04.812 --> 00:08:05.963
He signed a promise

00:08:05.987 --> 00:08:08.738
to help the people of Bali
say no to plastic bags.

00:08:08.762 --> 00:08:09.916
And we are now friends,

00:08:09.940 --> 00:08:11.336
and on a regular basis,

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:14.657
we remind him and his team
of the promises he has made.

00:08:15.372 --> 00:08:16.523
And indeed,

00:08:16.547 --> 00:08:18.453
recently he stated and committed

00:08:18.477 --> 00:08:23.120
that Bali will be
plastic bag free by 2018.

00:08:23.144 --> 00:08:29.980
(Applause)